@NODE INFO "IMPORTANT READING ABOUT THE END OF THE CHART..."
  @{B}׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳@{UB}
  @{BG FILL}     tHe iNTERNATiONAl fEDERATiOn oF fREe tRADERs iN cYBERSPACe !!     @{BG BACKGROUND}
  @{B}׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳=׳X׳@{UB}

                 @{FG HIGHLIGHT}THE iFFTic GOTHENBURG TRADER CHART DIED!@{FG TEXT}

        We don't have the energy and motivation to make it anymore!
       12 Boards will be just too much for us to handle in our way.
    When we can't improve ourselves anymore, we rather drop the matter!

                     @{FG HIGHLIGHT}NO TEARS, NO ANGER AND NO REGRETS@{FG TEXT}

  We also know now, that it can be both unfair and unfriendly to remove
  boards from the Chart. That's why we won't pick the best and leave the
  rest! We rather keep the friendship, cause that's what got us started!

    This might sound a bit sad or bitter, but Hey! friendship did Win!
  A victory like that can't be bad! So save your tears for worse things!

                  @{FG HIGHLIGHT}ALL GOOD THINGS HAS TO COME TO AN END!@{FG TEXT}

       Who knows what the future might bring? There will be lots of
     unreleased activities and restless fingers in iFFTic for a while!
     Maybe we will come up with something new to do, maybe a disk-mag?

                @{FG HIGHLIGHT}THE SCENE IS CHANGING, SO WHY SHOULDN'T WE!@{FG TEXT}

    Hey we didn't decide to terminate the Chart for any single reason!
    There's lots of reasons for us to move on to something different!
         We were quite bored anyhow with doing the same old Chart!
          We don't believe the word CHART to be accurate anymore!
       It has been less than 50% Trader-Lists in the Charts lately!
       And GBG forces us to include all and maybe only? GBG-Boards!

                      @{FG HIGHLIGHT}THE CHART HAS PLAYED IT'S PART!@{FG TEXT}

    We were all quite fresh Traders when we started out 9 months ago!
   At that time, all that mattered was Fat Accounts and Lots of Bytes!
    All members of iFFTic have now achieved that, so why not move on?

                      @{FG HIGHLIGHT}IT PLAYED PRETTY WELL!, BUT NOW@{FG TEXT}

                      @{FG HIGHLIGHT}IT'S TIME TO RECYCLE OUR MINDS!@{FG TEXT}

