 @{fg highlight}@{b}·@{ub}@{fg text}
 Dale^X3m joined Alpha Flight.
 @{fg highlight}@{b}·@{ub}@{fg text}
 Pet Sematary accepted with some wonder to be in a Chart for GBG-Traders.
 @{fg highlight}@{b}·@{ub}@{fg text}
 Armani became CoSysop at A-base.
 @{fg highlight}@{b}·@{ub}@{fg text}
 Armani joined Alpha Flight.
 @{fg highlight}@{b}·@{ub}@{fg text}
 Yogi became CoSysop at DagCentral 90210.
 @{fg highlight}@{b}·@{ub}@{fg text}
 Slash joined iFFTic again. We missed him and he wanted back. His handle
 will go back to Slash/Citron. iFFTic is happy to have the Party Man back!
 @{fg highlight}@{b}·@{ub}@{fg text}
 Tyson left iFFTic and joined account with Freud. Their new account is
 Tyson ^ Freud and they intend to stay Independent until they get an offer
 they can't refuse. iFFTic will miss Tyson, who was a real nice guy, a good
 friend and a very funny guy to have around! We will never forget the "lame-
 chat" or some of his other crazy but always friendly stunts! Way to go Man!
 @{fg highlight}@{b}·@{ub}@{fg text}
 Tyson ^ Freud replaced Tyson/iTc as CoSysop at Unicorn.
 @{fg highlight}@{b}·@{ub}@{fg text}
 Crime Zone is now running on dual nodes! Warez & Go, a 2-1 experience!
 @{fg highlight}@{b}·@{ub}@{fg text}
 iFFTic decided to terminate the GBG-TRADER CHART and felt quite good about
 it. Now we will start to plan for something completely different...
