@NODE CORRECT " CORRECTIONS FROM THE PREVIOUS CHART !!!"

                 @{FG HIGHLIGHT}SOME CORRECTIONS FROM THE PREVIOUS CHART!@{FG TEXT}

 REBEL was sad to read that we accused him of not presenting the results
 from his compo at TRANCENTRAL! We were wrong! He did write a mezz about it
 and he even did it the first day after the Compo! The reason both me and
 Sandman & some other users missed it was because we were expecting an Eall-
 message! iFFTic asks for some understanding on our fatal blunder here and
 kindly asks all sysops to write Ealls on issues like this, cause there's
 many of us that hardly ever bother to hit "r" to read through old letters!

@ENDNODE

@NODE THOUGHTS "DID YOU EXPECT US TO HAVE NO SHIT AT ALL? :)"

                  @{BG FILL} OUT WITH THE BAD - IN WITH THE GOOD! @{BG BACKGROUND}

        Sysops have been trying to tell us how to write our Chart,
        which Boards to include and which Boards never to include!
          Sysops have been telling us this and that without ever
             asking us for Our reasons to do it, and for Whom!

                 We have always done the CHART for USERS!!
              A CHART made by USERS for fellow USERS/TRADERS!
       Why on earth should we have wanted to do a CHART for Sysops??

   The trying to be helpful-guys have told us to skip all negative news.
    We have had about less than 5% negative news and about 90% of them
      have concerned bad management from Sysops! Is that so terrible?
    We just thought it to be Good information for USERS that are still
      choosing which Boards to join up on or which to really Pump on!

  The only other negative thing has been the Lamest choices in the Vote.
    We all know now that lots of users vote like idiots, and that some
     call all Vote-sites & even creates fake-users, just to vote with.
      We agree on that matter, that it's unfair to be branded lamest
        anything, when the voting can be manipulated quite a lot by
        overactive voters. We won't make that mistake again, kids!!

         Most iFFTic members started out trading, for quite a long
        time, on PD-boards before feeling good enough to go "Elite"
      Our expectation was that everything should be better and more 
    professional than on the PD-scene. The thing about PD is that it's
  runned by an idealist, who has it as his hobby, and wants to share it!
  The thing about "Elite" should be different we had been told! It were
     going to be your skill and your speed of delivery that counted!
        And that if you screw up, you would be punished! Even slow
           understanding or writing to much in swedish or just
              making the board look unCool could delete you!

     So we entered this scene quite prepared, but HO! what a surprise
      we were  going to have! Some boards in the "Elite"-Scene would
        die like a fish on dry land if it were out in the PD-Scene!

     A SYStem OPerator is Not just a Guy with a Modem and a Computer!
          A SYStem OPerator is the Engineer behind the Machine!!
              A SYStem OPerator is the Personality that makes
                You choose his Board before similar Boards.
              (Yes! there's plenty of Boards in both scenes)
   A SYStem OPerator is the Pilot of the Plane we are the passengers of!
                Come on baby! Lets Crash together! or what?

               Ungratefulness is the reward from the world.
        That's how we feel towards those people pointing out a few
     negative parts of the chart! We have delivered 9 big Charts with
  lots of this and that to everyone. Shouldn't that give us any credits?
    OK! we are not! complaining on all our Readers, many already agrees
    with us! But we have recieved so few direct thanx or greetz that it
     hurts to get more shit than kandy, when we gave You the opposite!

       But we believe ourselves to have been quite popular anyhow...
    Like lots of voters and maybe some more activities on the boards...

        So we might start something New later on, but then we will
            STATE CLEARLY who or which it will be made for and
                   why we have chosen to publish it...!

                 That "next production" will kind of prove
            how many disliking guys there really is out there!

  SO DO US A FAVOUR! DON'T READ WHAT WE PUBLISH! IF YOU ARE TO SENSITIVE!
  (not even if we change style, hahaha, cause we will never be reliable?)

                  @{BG FILL} OUT WITH THE BAD - IN WITH THE GOOD! @{BG BACKGROUND}

@ENDNODE

