 @{FG HIGHLIGHT}LOTS OF gREETz TO THE FOLLOWING BOARDS:@{FG TEXT}

 @{B}A-BASE ·@{UB} Thanx for the Capri-Party, Great Cre8ion!
 @{B}ASYLUM ·@{UB} Hey! You're a Comet! Which galaxy is your limit?
 @{B}BLACK LODGE ·@{UB} Thanx Mammoth! for not making a comeback! :)
