 @{B}CRIME ZONE ·@{UB} iFFTic domination here. Thanx for the Majors, Blade!
 @{B}DAGCENTRAL 9o21o ·@{UB} This was the coolest Board when we started out!
 @{B}HIDEOUT ·@{UB} Bad oh Bad, has your PC made you mute out of frustration?
 @{B}PET SEMATARY ·@{UB} This Board should have been included ages ago! Sorry!
 @{B}SANCTUARY ·@{UB} Oh! Where would iFFTic have been without ENTER THE SANDMAN?
